{"tid":1439063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文字藝術師] 不是催淚煙，是催淚彈毒氣 。不要小字報，要大字報。","createTime":"2019-08-10T03:44:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T04:47:43.000Z","uid":202716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"26041475c49f8b0648cb21cc246faebfdc73d0f6","tid":1439063,"uid":202716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:44:42.000Z","msg":"八月五日之後，文宣戰係目前最大既戰線。<br />\n以下係同身邊朋友/ 長輩討論後既意見。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><ins>1. 文字藝術 - 用詞 : 例: 不是催淚煙，是催淚彈毒氣</ins></strong></span><br />\n仲記唔記得雨傘果陣我地屌左<strong>催淚煙</strong>呢個字好耐?<br />\n政府就係利用<strong>催淚煙</strong>呢個字，令到成件事好似好細殺傷力。<br />\n我地必須要繼續堅持<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「催淚彈」</span></strong>，催淚彈係炮彈 ! <br />\n要指那陣煙霧，請用<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「催淚彈毒煙」或「催淚彈毒氣」，簡稱「毒煙」</span></strong>，聯合國列明是有毒既化學武器！<br />\n例如<br />\n原標題係「鄺葆賢等研記者吸催淚氣後症狀 逾 95 % 久咳咳血 728 比 612 清場嚴重」<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣應為「記者吸催淚彈毒氣後症狀 逾 95 % 久咳咳血」</span></strong><br />\n要記住，好多人(真係好多)未吸過催淚彈毒氣，以為果陣煙只係攻鼻剌眼既煙<br />\n都唔會覺得催淚彈可以打死人，因為佢睇CCTVB 只見催淚煙唔知開槍果下!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">2. 針對源頭，主導話語權</span></strong></ins><br />\n建制已經盡全力將香港混亂歸究示威者，即使有白衫打人，唔少人都比人spin 左去只要<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">黑衫唔搞事---&gt; 白衫唔出黎----&gt; 咩事都冇</span></strong>  既思維。我地一定要將源頭帶番政府，呼籲市民認清始作俑者，官逼民反。呢方面已經有唔少手足做緊。<br />\n例子:<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">通緝失蹤者林奠、打倒警黑共治新秩序、全民清算黑警、沒有暴徒只有暴政、示威只針對警署沒破壞一間商舖&hellip;&hellip;</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">3. 不要小字報，要大字報。</span></strong></ins><br />\n而家發展到街上面成日都見唔少文宣貼左係各式各樣既地方，但，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">好多D 字真係好撚細!!!!!</span></strong></span><br />\n對於事先知道既日子既活動，建議<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>貼大大隻字</strong></span>提所有人。<br />\n另外，<br />\n現時通街貼既細字文宣<ins>Target audience: 手足，會肯睇字會思考既淺藍黃</ins><br />\n其實有好大班人永遠掂行掂過，我地要搵方法將我地既信息入佢地腦。<br />\n例如<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大字報</span>，呢件事好中共但可以試下有冇用。<br />\n可以貼大大隻<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">通緝失蹤者林奠</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">抗議黑警使用過期催淚彈毒氣</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span></strong><br />\n簡單講，就係標題黨。我地媒體既標題入唔到佢地既電話電視，<br />\n唯有出現係佢地既生活入面。迫一班唔會主動睇我地D野既人，每日都見到。<br />\n將我地既信息入佢地腦。<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6ede2b2897ba34547e362ecd07eb49c10dc8d96f","tid":1439063,"uid":202716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:45:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2cbf3da2868044ed2feafab5a007fff753818ec","tid":1439063,"uid":202716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:46:46.000Z","msg":"Push!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"be36632dbd65338869f700dbc57d6da38f646ba7","tid":1439063,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:50:13.000Z","msg":"緊急！關於港島東反送中反黑大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1439067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1439067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"575576d48b915ecdd2bb88d3bf3e01b2ae21b4f1","tid":1439063,"uid":202716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:50:18.000Z","msg":"pUSH!!!!"},{"pid":"9f3435176c888557e8132b210b49f878c4820419","tid":1439063,"uid":202716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:01:48.000Z","msg":"pUSH!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"a6680e9c554afccde3c66466e9421c09e1252774","tid":1439063,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:47:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><em><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各自努力<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></ins></em></strong><br />\n唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人重點日程：<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月9-11日</strong>：機場和你飛&bull;萬人接機&bull;一連三日(1300)</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月10日</strong>：銀髮族遞信「900警總」&gt;「1000律政司辦公室」&gt;「1100特首辦」<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：守護孩子未來親子遊行（1030愛丁堡廣場）<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：大埔遊行（1400大埔巴士總站）（反對通知書）</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月11日</strong>：港島東遊行（1300維多利亞公園）<br />\n<strong>8月11日</strong>：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">逢星期五，日擺買！減少家庭支出</span></strong></span>"}]}